Heineken Cup Rugby 2013 Final Awarded to Dublin’s Aviva Stadium

-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 
2011-06-09T12:56:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-09/heineken-cup-rugby-2013-final-awarded-to-dublin-s-aviva-stadium.html
The 2013 Heineken Cup rugby final
will be played at Aviva Stadium in Dublin, tournament organizer
European Rugby Cup said.  The championship match of  Europe ’s elite club competition
will return to Ireland’s capital for the first time since 2003,
when Toulouse beat Perpignan 22-17 at Landsdowne Road stadium.  Dublin-based Leinster defeated  Leicester Tigers  and
Toulouse at Aviva Stadium last season en route to a 33-22 win
over Northampton in the final at Cardiff’s Millennium Stadium.
The 2012 Heineken Cup final will be played at Twickenham Stadium
in London.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  